  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge</h2><strong>Draw IT!</strong> is precision-demanding VR puzzle game. Help a little ball reach it's destination by drawing way and avoiding obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/f20208255f495cb71070f68821a47ae2.poster.avif?t=1643319766\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/f20208255f495cb71070f68821a47ae2.webm?t=1643319766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/f20208255f495cb71070f68821a47ae2.mp4?t=1643319766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adjust ball speed and compete in leaderboards</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/ad2dc7cc1a06234fd1258ffc8924f806.poster.avif?t=1643319766\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/ad2dc7cc1a06234fd1258ffc8924f806.webm?t=1643319766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/ad2dc7cc1a06234fd1258ffc8924f806.mp4?t=1643319766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Creative Mode</h2>And when you are done with all this levels or just prefer casual experience then immerse yourself in <strong>Creative Mode!</strong><br>A lot more paint is also more ideas. You are limited only by your imagination!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620360/extras/e056ed95d730a4b39f19dc74e464e6d4.p